00:01:35.610 --> 00:01:36.110
Thank you.

00:01:36.110 --> 00:01:38.750
You're going to have a chance
to weigh in on the things you've

00:01:38.750 --> 00:01:41.540
heard and other things
that you are thinking

00:01:41.540 --> 00:01:44.580
about in your own schools,
and we'll go from there

00:01:44.580 --> 00:01:46.260
in terms of discussion.

00:01:46.260 --> 00:01:48.090
So improving teaching.

00:01:48.090 --> 00:01:50.390
There's sort of two
approaches sometimes.

00:01:50.390 --> 00:01:52.526
The fortune cookie approach.

00:01:52.526 --> 00:01:55.090
Teachers work with the
