00:01:58.310 --> 00:02:01.550
And that's important, but it's
probably not the whole thing.

00:02:01.550 --> 00:02:03.350
And then there's the other side.

00:02:03.350 --> 00:02:04.940
I will adopt best
practices, which

00:02:04.940 --> 00:02:07.420
